Abstract = {{In this paper we develop a generic hierarchical model for performance
   analysis of intrusion detection techniques as applied to a
   cyber-physical system (CPS) consisting of mobile nodes with navigation,
   manipulation, sensing and actuating capability. We develop two intrusion
   detection techniques, namely, positional discontinuity and
   enviroconsistency, for intrusion detection of malicious attackers in a
